{
  "stem": "5810.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was buried in the backyard, because I knew that place best.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And whenever it was necessary to pay them, in view of the fact that if we had had the whole money with us, they would have taken it away from us, and then we would be of no further use to them.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was on a monthly basis that I used to go to the house and unbury one piece and go ahead and pay them.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But I saw that dwindling.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And there came a time, close to the time of liberation, 1944, [INAUDIBLE], that we were going to run out of this money.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we didn't know what was going to be, what was going to happen to us once this money ran out.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We knew very well that they weren't doing it because they wanted to save us.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We knew their feeling then.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We knew what they had put us through.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We knew what we were going through.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And by the way, in the middle of all this. to go back to the school, I had become quite the Catholic.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I, since I was going to mass daily, and it was Catholic priests that were teaching the classes and so on.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "It was no longer something I was doing by design.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I believed in it, and I believed in it very strongly, to a point I remember that one of the games, if you want to call it games, that the kids played on the street, whenever there was a allied bombing-- Whether it was the British or the Americans that were bombing Brussels, Belgium-- we were hiding in doorways-- not then shelters.",
      "word_count": 62
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And the biggest thing was to pick up the shrapnel-- a collection of shrapnel for us.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
